node.text:
To celebrate Black History Month going into Women’s History Month, I partnered with Martell to create a trunk highlighting some Phenomenal products from black female owned companies to gift to some phenomenal women who continuously are making strides in their respective fields.

I toast you & honor you ladies, And I hope you enjoy your gift. #MakeYourStatement 💜 

Products Included: @coolcoffeeclique, @labeautyologist, @shopherlistic, @sosheargenius, @thecrayoncase, @itsbrowngirljane & @culturetags

node.text:
All my fellow Black Female Bosses, you don’t want to miss all of the gems that will be dropped at Fearless VC Week taking place August 23rd- August 29th, 2021. 

They will be educating Black Women Entrepreneurs and Venture Capitalists along with hosting a $50,000 grant pitch competition. 

@fearless.fund VC Week is a multigenerational hybrid event taking place in Atlanta, GA and virtually. 
The Women Investors Track Day will be hosted by @ally on Friday, August 27th, 2021 at Southern Exchange Ballroom, where they will be encouraging women to become diverse investors to take lead and change the face of the Venture Capital space.

Visit www.fearless.fund and click on VC Week to get your in-person or virtual tickets!

#FearlessFund #FearlessVCWeek #WomenEntrepreneurs #WomenInvestors #VCWeek #WomenEntrepreneurBusinessGrant #BusinessGrant #VentureCapital #Entrepreneurship #Investors
